description:
Class is in session. Gisele Bündchen has a perfect life and she wants to teach you the lessons she’s learned along the way. From kicking off her modeling career at 14 years old to becoming a top model and a full on celebrity by age 20, she’s lived and learned and now that wisdom is ours. Thanks a lot.
